  "texts": [
    "Details regarding DNA sequence design are described in the included supplementary materials.",
    "Subsequent activity screening of these sequences in triplicate showed that nearly a third of Round 1 sequences met the objective better than the best variant in the initial, randomly selected set (Fig. 3B).",
    "The best variant in the Round 1 library, MKFNY (W56M Y57K L59F Q60N F89Y), demonstrated a total cyclopropanation yield of 93% and a cis:trans selectivity ratio of 12:1.",
    "We then gave the newly collected data back to the ALDE computational algorithm for a second round of active learning.",
    "The top 90 predicted sequences were again synthesized and tested exactly as before (Round 2, Fig. 3C)."
